headline: Three Reasons to Avoid DAL and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Delta Air Lines’s 29.8% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 19.9%, and its stock price has climbed to $62.56 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
